item.title: Create a QR code that shows Suki Oishii Suki by scratch
item.description: ["Oishiizumi Suki" Advent Calendar](https://qiita.com/advent-calendar/2019/ohishi-izumi-suki) I will be in charge of the 5th day. This is my first time to join the Advent Calendar. I get excited. This time, I will introduce the procedure to create a QR code from scratch without depending on the existing library. It is not particularly useful now that the existing libraries are substantial, but please read it as a reading material that feels that QR code is created like this.
